        <title>WordPress 主题 Bliss 修改 Material Design 配色</title>
        <link>https://umi.im/wordpress-theme-material-design/</link>
        <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2015 19:58:46 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://umi.im/wordpress-theme-material-design/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;我现在使用的博客主题是 Bluthemes 开发的 Bliss 主题，极简卡片式的风格，用主题自带的蓝色主题。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;a-hrefhttpthemeforestnetitembliss-personal-minimalist-wordpress-blog-theme5423780-target_blankbliss--personal-minimalist-wordpress-blog-themea&#34;&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#a-hrefhttpthemeforestnetitembliss-personal-minimalist-wordpress-blog-theme5423780-target_blankbliss--personal-minimalist-wordpress-blog-themea&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;http://themeforest.net/item/bliss-personal-minimalist-wordpress-blog-theme/5423780&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Bliss | Personal Minimalist WordPress Blog Theme&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/old-Bliss-wordpress-theme.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-4248&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/old-Bliss-wordpress-theme.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;old-Bliss-wordpress-theme&#34; width=&#34;936&#34; height=&#34;686&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/old-Bliss-wordpress-theme.jpg 936w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/old-Bliss-wordpress-theme-150x110.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/old-Bliss-wordpress-theme-300x220.jpg 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最近，在物色  WordPress  主题的时候发现一个 Material Design 的主题的网站 &lt;a href=&#34;http://MaterialWP.com&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;MaterialWP.com&lt;/a&gt; ，很喜欢这网站首页配色。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/materialwp-com.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-4250&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/materialwp-com.png&#34; alt=&#34;materialwp-com&#34; width=&#34;1081&#34; height=&#34;782&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/materialwp-com.png 1081w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/materialwp-com-150x109.png 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/materialwp-com-300x217.png 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/materialwp-com-1024x741.png 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1081px) 100vw, 1081px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;开始研究怎么把 Bliss 主题改成那种配色，首先得知道人家网站的颜色的 Hex 颜色代码，用 QQ 截图把光标移动到需要的颜色上能得到 RGB 颜色代码（ 48,63,159 ）。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/QQ-RGB-HEX.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-4252&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/QQ-RGB-HEX.png&#34; alt=&#34;QQ-RGB-HEX&#34; width=&#34;579&#34; height=&#34;334&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/QQ-RGB-HEX.png 579w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/QQ-RGB-HEX-150x87.png 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/QQ-RGB-HEX-300x173.png 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 579px) 100vw, 579px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;用在线工具把 RGB 代码转换成为 Hex 代码（ #303F9F ）。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/RGB-TO-HEX.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-4254&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/RGB-TO-HEX.png&#34; alt=&#34;RGB-TO-HEX&#34; width=&#34;884&#34; height=&#34;423&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/RGB-TO-HEX.png 884w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/RGB-TO-HEX-150x72.png 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/RGB-TO-HEX-300x144.png 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 884px) 100vw, 884px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后修改 Style.css ，技术太渣，怎么改都没用。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;用最笨的方法，我找到了 Bliss 主题自定义 CSS 的文件，在主题目录下的 inc 目录的 custom-css.php ，在此文件的第 44 行开始。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&#34;lang:php decode:true&#34;&gt;case &#39;default&#39;;	
			$css_options[&#39;theme_color&#39;] 							= &#39;#45b0ee&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;background_color&#39;] 					= &#39;#EDEDED&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;top_banner_color&#39;] 					= &#39;#444444&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;top_banner_font_color&#39;] 		= &#39;#FFFFFF&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;top_banner_social_color&#39;]		= &#39;#FFFFFF&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;header_color&#39;] 							= &#39;#FFFFFF&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;header_font_color&#39;] 				= &#39;#777777&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;post_header_color&#39;] 				= &#39;#333333&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;main_font_color&#39;] 				= &#39;#333333&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;widget_header_color&#39;] 			= &#39;#FFFFFF&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;widget_header_font_color&#39;] 	= &#39;#333333&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;footer_color&#39;] 							= &#39;#333333&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;footer_header_color&#39;] 			= &#39;#FFFFFF&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;footer_font_color&#39;] 				= &#39;#FFFFFF&#39;;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;需要修改的是 theme_color （主题）、 background_color （背景）、 top_banner_color （顶部）、header_color （导航栏）和 footer_color （低部）的颜色。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;参照 &lt;a href=&#34;http://MaterialWP.com&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;MaterialWP.com&lt;/a&gt; 的颜色，我的改成了这样：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Top Banner：&lt;span style=&#34;color: #3f51b5;&#34;&gt;#3F51B5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background ：&lt;span style=&#34;color: #e5e5e5;&#34;&gt;#E5E5E5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Header： &lt;span style=&#34;color: #303f9f;&#34;&gt;#303F9F&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Footer：&lt;span style=&#34;color: #374147;&#34;&gt;#374147&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;pre class=&#34;lang:php decode:true&#34;&gt;case &#39;default&#39;;	
			$css_options[&#39;theme_color&#39;] 							= &#39;#4450C0&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;background_color&#39;] 					= &#39;#E5E5E5&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;top_banner_color&#39;] 					= &#39;#3F51B5&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;top_banner_font_color&#39;] 		= &#39;#FFFFFF&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;top_banner_social_color&#39;]		= &#39;#FFFFFF&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;header_color&#39;] 							= &#39;#303F9F&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;header_font_color&#39;] 				= &#39;#FFFFFF&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;post_header_color&#39;] 				= &#39;#212121&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;main_font_color&#39;] 				= &#39;#333333&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;widget_header_color&#39;] 			= &#39;#FFFFFF&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;widget_header_font_color&#39;] 	= &#39;#333333&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;footer_color&#39;] 							= &#39;#374147&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;footer_header_color&#39;] 			= &#39;#374147&#39;;
			$css_options[&#39;footer_font_color&#39;] 				= &#39;#EEEEEE&#39;;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;改完颜色顺眼了很多，但是 Chrome 下字体都是宋体，在主题设置页自定义 CSS 里面添加这样一段就能把全部字体变成微软雅黑。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&#34;lang:css decode:true&#34;&gt;/* Primary Font Style */
                body, .font1, .font-primary, .commentlist, input{
                        font-family:Microsoft YaHei,Georgia, &#39;冬青黑体简体中文 w3&#39;, Times, serif;
                }

        /* Header Font Style */
                h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, .site-title{
                        font-family:Microsoft YaHei,Georgia, &#39;冬青黑体简体中文 w3&#39;, Times, serif;
                }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;装修好后特意上 OS X 上截个图，黑苹果的妙用…&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/2015-Baka-House.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-4241&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/2015-Baka-House.png&#34; alt=&#34;2015-Baka-House&#34; width=&#34;1408&#34; height=&#34;1059&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/2015-Baka-House.png 1408w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/2015-Baka-House-150x113.png 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/2015-Baka-House-300x226.png 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/2015-Baka-House-1024x770.png 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
        </item>
